  metaDescription: "Canadian Alternative Minimum Tax (AMT) under ITA Part I Div E.1 s127.5-127.55. 2024 reforms: 20.5% rate (was 15%), $173,205 exemption (was $40k). Capital gains 100% inclusion. Stock option deduction reversed. Donation credit 50%. AMT credit carryforward applies. Confirmed April 2026.",
